# PYDownloader

**PYDownloader** is an advanced, lightweight, async file downloader built using Python and `aiohttp`, featuring:

- 🔄 Pause/Resume support  
- 📶 Live speed & progress tracking  
- 📥 Multi-format download (ZIP, MP4, MP3, etc.)
- 🖼️ Beautiful dark-themed UI (using `ttkbootstrap`)
- 🎮 System tray minimization support
- 🔔 Sound notification on download completion
- 🧠 Smart retry and resume support

---

## 🔧 Requirements

Install all dependencies using:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt

python downloader.py

Compiling to EXE (Using PyInstaller)
Use the following one-liner to build the app:
##
pyinstaller --onefile --windowed --icon=icon.ico --add-data "add.png;." --add-data "start.png;." --add-data "pause.png;." --add-data "stop.png;." --add-data "remove.png;." --add-data "download.png;." --name PYDownloader downloader.py
##
compiled in dist folder

Creating an Installer (Using Inno Setup)
Install Inno Setup

Save the following script as downloader_installer.iss in your project root:

Open this .iss file with Inno Setup and click Compile.

Your final installer will be saved as:

Output\PYDownloader-setup.exe


**added a test file for testing or editing


